tint - tree-sitter powered linter

- Running: `tint lint`
- Config: Sample file available in `.tint.lint.sample` (default loc is `.tint.lint`)
- Output format: `filename:start-line:start-col:end-line:end-col: message`
- Example output: `src/internal/kopia/data_collection.go:98:14:98:25: do not use clues.WrapWC if ctx is passed into the func`

